   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from grmtools.data.io import load_evt\n",
    "from grmtools.data.lightcurve import LightCurve, CountLightCurve\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from astropy.io import fits\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "## Load photons from L1 data,\n",
    "## detector = 2\n",
    "## gain_type = 'low'\n",
    "evt = load_evt(\"../../../examples/data/gbg_evt_tn210121_184148_gb_v00.fits\", full_load=False, det_list=[2], gain_type='low')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "2248d008-26c7-4a6f-b86b-6a8bd5eaf333",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Count Light Curve (CLC)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "e9be0d8c-1d26-4110-b10e-41852c1ff37b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 720x576 with 0 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 576x432 with 6 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "## Generate Lightcurve object from Event, time resolution is 3 sec (not equal-width at rightmost edge)\n",
    "lc = evt.to_lightcurve(resolution=0.1)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Plot\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10,8))\n",
    "lc.plot(color='blue', GUI=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e7116b65-95b3-49fb-8982-452da03a5141",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Background selection\n",
    "One can use GUI to interactively select time range as background data, or use the method `LightCurve.background_range_list`,\n",
    "example:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "f2675ca7-5dc1-4b6e-864f-65f16e0860e4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 576x432 with 6 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "T0 = lc.trigger_time\n",
    "lc.background_range_list = [[T0, T0+50], [T0+200, T0+250]]\n",
    "lc.plot(color='blue', GUI=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d22fcdcd-1d10-4d4d-8414-d6e802b91345",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Cumulative Count Light curve (CCLC)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "68749870-99ed-47af-9297-3eff911f2b70",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 720x576 with 0 Axes>"
      ]

     "output_type": "display_data"
